@startuml
title Shape と Shader への値の渡し分け

'left to right direction
top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "色 / テクスチャ\n法線マップ" as ColorParams
rectangle "ambient / specular\npower / emissive" as LightingParams
rectangle "has_bone\nweight_debug" as DebugParams
rectangle "Shape.materialParams\n-> shader.doParameter()\n-> setter へ流す" as MaterialRouting #eef5ff
rectangle "light position" as LightPosition
rectangle "fog default" as FogDefault
rectangle "bind group / palette\nshared state" as SharedState

ColorParams --> MaterialRouting
LightingParams --> MaterialRouting
DebugParams --> MaterialRouting

MaterialRouting ..> LightPosition : 描画ごとに\n使い分け
MaterialRouting --> FogDefault
MaterialRouting --> SharedState

note top of ColorParams
オブジェクトごとの差として変わる値
end note

note top of LightPosition
複数 Shape で共有するほうが自然な値
end note
@enduml
